      <title>[2092] Consensus New Year</title>
      <link>https://xkcd.com/2092/</link>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <div>
            <a href="https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/consensus_new_year.png">
              <img src="https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/consensus_new_year.png" alt="The biggest jump is at 11:00am EST (4:00pm UTC) when midnight reaches the UTC+8 time zone. That time zone, which includes China, is home to a quarter of the world's population. India and Sri Lanka (UTC+5:30) put us over the 50% mark soon after." style="height: auto;" />
            </a>
            <p>The biggest jump is at 11:00am EST (4:00pm UTC) when midnight reaches the UTC+8 time zone. That time zone, which includes China, is home to a quarter of the world's population. India and Sri Lanka (UTC+5:30) put us over the 50% mark soon after.</p>
